WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'ColorBarr' is another of my Workbench games. In this game, you
have to create 8 rows of coloured tiles in such a way that each
row has tiles of the same colour.

  In some game levels, some of the rows contains a few tiles,
where other rows have as many as 15 tiles, so it's up to you to
decide where each type of coloured tiles go on which row. Note
that 2 rows of tiles can have tiles of the same colour...

  Try to complete each of the game levels in the least amount of
moves.

  Have fun!

